{"tid":151891,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"東京旅行求屌","createTime":"2017-03-11T09:24:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-11T12:36:53.000Z","uid":3164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e3882d521d89d6428c803a03f38890d5ef1ec580","tid":151891,"uid":3164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T09:24:57.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n5月中會同女友去東京玩6日5夜<br />\n大家都係第一次去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n暫定行程如下<br />\n第一日 新宿行街<br />\n第二日 迪士尼樂園<br />\n第三日 貓島<br />\n第四&amp;五日 淺草，行街<br />\n第六日 早機返香港<br />\n<br />\n行程大致上係咁 <br />\n咁我最唔熟個一點就黎喇<br />\n就係點搭jr去迪士尼<br />\n<br />\n上網睇過最直接係搭去東京站再轉京葉線去舞濱 <br />\n但聽人講係東京站搵路都搵死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以搵左第條路<br />\n就係由新宿去新木楊再去舞濱 咁就轉一次車就得<br />\n<br />\n咁係咪的係新宿站買一張飛去舞濱就ok? <br />\n搭臨海線（定係崎京線？）去到大崎繼續坐係車就會到新木場？ 到左新木場就轉去京葉線月台？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大鄉里第一次出城請各巴絲打指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24d903429553e77961f52936648d7fd8347fc309","tid":151891,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T09:50:13.000Z","msg":"池袋 涉谷都唔會去？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"084aa3c3e019e6d7ad995be5c6dce7520c51d474","tid":151891,"uid":66951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T09:55:15.000Z","msg":"東京站好易搵 有哂指示<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8891cef826047bd367b26d7a36420ba2a998131","tid":151891,"uid":3164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T09:55:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>池袋 涉谷都唔會去？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第一同最尾兩日都會係東京周圍走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dd6d41dd4fcbd4683c310dec22904e9d9205265","tid":151891,"uid":3164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T09:56:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>東京站好易搵 有哂指示<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為上網睇啲人都係提議搭臨海線去 話轉車方便啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"320dcbbe5abd0aa38ec30a9cd423cd1ba43beffc","tid":151891,"uid":3416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T09:57:22.000Z","msg":"屌你呢啲叫行程？<br />\n整個excel<br />\n列好曬幾點去邊 搭咩車 預算先講啦"},{"pid":"cb4e9b0a06c8b2a0f7819a11c4abb1641fc5b846","tid":151891,"uid":66951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T10:00:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>東京站好易搵 有哂指示<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為上網睇啲人都係提議搭臨海線去 話轉車方便啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我記得去迪士尼都坐好耐 你新宿上應該唔係站頭？去玩一日 無位坐都幾係野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07a6b4cf45a938c9c2d1f27981246e2063d7b9e1","tid":151891,"uid":3164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T10:02:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你呢啲叫行程？<br />\n整個excel<br />\n列好曬幾點去邊 搭咩車 預算先講啦</blockquote><br />\n整好左冇放上黎唔使咁勞氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n主要係唔清楚點搭車去迪士尼所以想問問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92aea80529a986dc4dba3a931541eb495b91d1ee","tid":151891,"uid":3164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T10:03:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>東京站好易搵 有哂指示<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為上網睇啲人都係提議搭臨海線去 話轉車方便啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我記得去迪士尼都坐好耐 你新宿上應該唔係站頭？去玩一日 無位坐都幾係野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去程應該唔怕嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n回程都諗過攰就坐巴士直返新宿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去程唔坐巴士主因係怕佢耐<br />\n睇過差唔多搭成個鐘<br />\n而搭鐵路就大約40分鐘度<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"416cce6c2be6ea95ba654402e7530842638144b3","tid":151891,"uid":15404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T10:05:49.000Z","msg":"你指嘅貓島即係江之島？<br />\n<br />\n2016年5月都去過，無想像中咁好<br />\n<br />\n如果只係為影張相，咁真係無必要囉。。。<br />\n<br />\n而且無乜貓。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，迪士尼放後d，第4/5日<br />\n<br />\n因為玩同排隊消耗極高體力<br />\n<br />\n玩完第日會好攰，起唔到身。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後，建議你去outlet行下，好多驚喜架"},{"pid":"3154285c3e7e95ae70f535d93202f55fb2ad3f8b","tid":151891,"uid":3164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T10:10:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你指嘅貓島即係江之島？<br />\n<br />\n2016年5月都去過，無想像中咁好<br />\n<br />\n如果只係為影張相，咁真係無必要囉。。。<br />\n<br />\n而且無乜貓。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，迪士尼放後d，第4/5日<br />\n<br />\n因為玩同排隊消耗極高體力<br />\n<br />\n玩完第日會好攰，起唔到身。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後，建議你去outlet行下，好多驚喜架</blockquote><br />\n係呀 去江之島 <br />\n因為我地都鐘意貓 又諗住去近郊放鬆下所以揀呢度<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n揀第二日係因為呢日係星期五 <br />\n想避開星期六，日（即係第三，四日）嘅人潮 而第五日（星期一）夜晚又要入機場 <br />\n所以揀呢日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7d9096c9b15a24f71fb55d4961524ac9213b5c0","tid":151891,"uid":17524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T10:30:42.000Z","msg":"台場唔去？ 幾舒服架"},{"pid":"04fded2c46d397f04521ffc2d18ecf5e8df3e900","tid":151891,"uid":3164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T10:48:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>台場唔去？ 幾舒服架</blockquote><br />\n去台場好定貓島好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淨係知台場有高達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc7af9d767677629f88396d3da4b34cf781a7098","tid":151891,"uid":88118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T11:25:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>台場唔去？ 幾舒服架</blockquote><br />\n去台場好定貓島好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淨係知台場有高達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n台場個高達冇左啦"},{"pid":"c54073374455ec29b36870ad8e22a4e964371248","tid":151891,"uid":26003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T11:29:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>台場唔去？ 幾舒服架</blockquote><br />\n去台場好定貓島好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淨係知台場有高達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n台場個高達冇左啦</blockquote><br />\n4月好似出獨角獸"},{"pid":"2bfbe8f5d3abe8261185a40be1d64fd2c51f7316","tid":151891,"uid":3164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T11:32:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>台場唔去？ 幾舒服架</blockquote><br />\n去台場好定貓島好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淨係知台場有高達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n台場個高達冇左啦</blockquote><br />\n4月好似出獨角獸</blockquote><br />\n其實行街唔知行邊好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aff4ddde423c54f5dd723d8727255e15dd5ccc39","tid":151891,"uid":41969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T11:36:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>東京站好易搵 有哂指示<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為上網睇啲人都係提議搭臨海線去 話轉車方便啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔會錯 好多指示<br />\n不過都行幾遠 個站大到痴線<br />\n睇你住邊囉 新新宿好似直頭有巴士去到<br />\nbtw如果係直接入樂園唔好on99搭果架迪迪尼地鐵<br />\n因為路程200m都唔知有無😂"},{"pid":"8d37aa45756e0ec94bc22bcfe7ed67aa3a74b65a","tid":151891,"uid":33528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T11:38:01.000Z","msg":"其實江之島行半日幾正<br />\n吹下海風睇下景都幾寫意<br />\n不過唔好預有太多貓 同埋預一日咁多喇<br />\n利申舊年去 得幾隻貓咁"},{"pid":"ce2e32d57077b437ac107aa999ffa14d12fd64d6","tid":151891,"uid":68598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T11:55:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實江之島行半日幾正<br />\n吹下海風睇下景都幾寫意<br />\n不過唔好預有太多貓 同埋預一日咁多喇<br />\n利申舊年去 得幾隻貓咁</blockquote><br />\n小貓3~4隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"029ebfe211fcf6e3b272842f75a948c53c21f2ad","tid":151891,"uid":3164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T12:36:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實江之島行半日幾正<br />\n吹下海風睇下景都幾寫意<br />\n不過唔好預有太多貓 同埋預一日咁多喇<br />\n利申舊年去 得幾隻貓咁</blockquote><br />\n小貓3~4隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好 明白了<br />\n但係去吹下海風都唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}